data.description: This is a must see! This perfect lake-front 4 Bedroom, 3 Bath home in the beautiful and gated community of Daniels Preserve in Gateway. This beautiful home features two master bedrooms! The 4th Bedroom/master is located upstairs and can also be used as a huge bonus room, with its own private full bathroom and separate central AC unit!! Master Suite downstairs includes a full walk-in closet, and separate shower and tub. This home has a brand new roof. Both AC units are newer and a new water heater has been installed. Newer stainless appliances, as well as many upgrades include tile flooring, granite counter tops, and a built-in bookcase in the Master Suite. Open floor plan for a wonderful entertaining space. This gated community includes many amenities, and is located near the new JetBlue Baseball Park, shopping, golfing, and biking.
